rows.label: tlk70000054_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Tales of your bravery have reached
us even here, you know.

rows.label: tlk70000054_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I don't think there's a soul in Iira
who doesn't know the names of Lord
Adel and Laura-sama.

rows.label: tlk70000054_05_msg0003
rows.name: We've got it well in hand here.

rows.label: tlk70000054_05_msg0004
rows.name:
If Aletta comes under threat, we
got plans to evacuate the civilians
to the Liberalitan Archipelago.

rows.label: tlk70000054_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Well then. Adel, everyone -
fair fortune all!
